Hello gangasters!

In celebration of India's 70th Independence day there shall be a series of
cultural activities from *8-8-16 through 14-8-16*. All activities shall be
based on patriotic themes. The entire general student body is invited to
take part in the same.

The events mentioned are considered as *pre-LitSoc events* where each
hostel gets points for participation. We expect a huge number of
enthusiastic participants from our hostel. So I kindly request all to
participate in these events and bring laurels to our beloved hostel.

Cheers!!!

VIBIN M
Social Secretary
Ganga Hostel
IIT Madras.

